data.description: This 5 bedroom, 5 level split offers so much living space. Over 4100 sq. ft. per Auditor. Situated on a .42 acre lot this wonderful open floor plan features a great rm w/gas fplc & vaulted ceiling, ex lg kitchen w/island, plenty of cab pantry & planning desk. French doors lead to formal din rm/office. 2nd level features owner's suite w/private deluxe bath & huge walk-in closet. 3 add bdrms are located on the 3rd level. A family rm & in-law/teen suite w/1/2 bath are located on the lower level & the fin 5th level flex room. Additonal  amenities include a convenient 1st flr ldry & mud room, side load garage, approx.1 yr old roof  & a generous size paver patio that completes the outdoor space.
